        <num>2906</num>
        <heading>Hospitals included</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_2906__subsec_i">
          <num>(i)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of the\nfederal public health service act, as amended, tuberculosis, mental,\nchronic disease, and other types of hospitals, including laboratories,\nout-patient departments, nurses' homes and training facilities, and\ncentral service facilities operated in connection with hospitals, but\ndoes not include any hospital furnishing primarily domiciliary care.\n</p>
